description: Lvpai Group Limited does not have significant operations. It intends to seek a business combination with an operating company in any number of industries or sectors. Previously, the company offered liquidity, technology solution, and brokerage services to professional traders, and FX brokers and partners. The company was formerly known as Finotec Group, Inc. and changed its name to Lvpai Group Limited in March 2021. Lvpai Group Limited was founded in 1987 and is based in Oceanside, New York.
